Rating: 0
I haven't made this as of yet, but I do make something quite similar. To one 14 oz can of chopped artichoke hearts I add 2/3 C chopped salami, 1/2 C shredded cheddar cheese, 1/2 C parmesan cheese, 1/2 C mayo, & 3 Tbs chopped green onions. Place in glass pie plate. Sprinkle w/1/4 C shredded cheddar cheese & about 1 T chopped green onions. Bake @ 350 for about 20 min until bubbly. Delicious!

